===Pronunciation===
חשׁך / chôshek / kho-shek'

===Etymology===
From חשׁך châshak {{HH|2821}}; 

===Noun===
'''חשׁך'''

# The [[dark]]; hence (literally) [[darkness]]; figuratively misery, destruction, death, ignorance, sorrow, wickedness: - dark (-ness), night, obscurity.

